PN,31501
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1777497070
OL,3,CCommon antidepressant recalled in the
OL,4,CUK after wrong medicine found in packet
OL,6,FMore than 80,000 packs of a commonly
OL,7,Fused antidepressant have been recalled
OL,8,Fafter a patient discovered the wrong
OL,9,Fmedicine inside their pack.
OL,11,FThe recall follows a complaint by a
OL,12,Fpatient who takes Sertraline 100 mg
OL,13,Ffilm-coated tablets and instead found
OL,14,Fa strip of another antidepressant,
OL,15,FCitalopram 40mg film-coated tablets,
OL,16,Finside the sealed box.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1777497070
OL,3,CCommon antidepressant recalled in the
OL,4,CUK after wrong medicine found in packet
OL,6,FBoth Sertraline and Citalopram are
OL,7,Fselective serotonin reuptake
OL,8,Finhibitors (SSRIs) used to treat
OL,9,Fdepression, anxiety disorders, and
OL,10,Frelated mental health conditions by
OL,11,Fboosting serotonin to the brain.
OL,13,FUK-based pharmaceutical company,
OL,14,FAmarox, has issued a "precautionary
OL,15,Frecall" of a particular batch of
OL,16,FSertraline, the Medicines and
OL,17,FHealthcare products Regulatory Agency
OL,18,F(MHRA) said.
OL,20,FThe same manufacturer produces both
OL,21,Fmedications at the same site.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1777497070
OL,3,CCommon antidepressant recalled in the
OL,4,CUK after wrong medicine found in packet
OL,6,FThe MHRA said that the manufacturing
OL,7,Ferror "appears to have occurred during
OL,8,Fsecondary packaging of the blister
OL,9,Fstrips into the cartons".
OL,11,FThey said that patients who have
OL,12,Falready taken any Citalopram 40mg
OL,13,Ftablets by mistake or are experiencing
OL,14,Fside effects should seek medical
OL,15,Fadvice immediately.
OL,26,@oD@GOUqD@XO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
