PN,31504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1777497070
OL,3,CCommon antidepressant recalled in the
OL,4,CUK after wrong medicine found in packet
OL,6,FThe MHRA said that pharmacists should
OL,7,Fstop supplying the batch and contact
OL,8,Fany patients who may have been
OL,9,Fdispensed the impacted product,
OL,10,FSertraline 100mg tablets batch number
OL,11,FV2500425.
OL,13,FThe regulator said 81,872 packs are
OL,14,Fincluded in the recall.
OL,16,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,17,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,18,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,19,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
