PN,31505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1777497070
OL,3,CCommon antidepressant recalled in the
OL,4,CUK after wrong medicine found in packet
OL,6,FDr Alison Cave, the MHRA's chief
OL,7,Fsafety officer, said: "If you have
OL,8,Fbeen prescribed Sertraline 100mg
OL,9,Ftablets and have received batch number
OL,10,FV2500425, please check the carton
OL,11,Fcontains the right medication.
OL,13,F"You can find the batch number and
OL,14,Fexpiry date printed on the side of the
OL,15,Fouter packaging.
OL,26,@oD@WOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/7
