FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1777497070
OL,3,CCommon antidepressant recalled in the
OL,4,CUK after wrong medicine found in packet
OL,6,F"If the blister strips inside the
OL,7,Fcarton are labelled Citalopram 40mg,
OL,8,Fplease contact your pharmacy as soon
OL,9,Fas possible. If they are labelled
OL,10,FSertraline 100mg, no further action is
OL,11,Fneeded.
OL,13,F"Patients who have accidentally taken
OL,14,FCitalopram instead of ` or as well as
OL,15,F` Sertraline may experience some
OL,16,Fheightened serotonergic side effects.
OL,18,F"These can include nausea, headache,
OL,19,Fsleep changes, and mild anxiety."
